name: Radiate
description:
Original artwork created in 2015 from the 'Memoryscapes' solo show at Absolute Art Gallery in Belgium. Made from film negatives, x-ray, computer parts and acrylic paint on recycled acrylic sheet with LED, mounted on aluminium panel. 

The materials used have been contributed by members of the public. A social art project, open to everyone. Find out how to recycle and include your obsolete materials in future artworks by getting in touch.
